  (∀ #t2 #t3.
    (LoggerAsserts( L1, sct1 ) @ #t2) ∧ (LoggerAsserts( L2, sct2 ) @ #t3)
   ⇒
    L1 = L2) ∧
  (∀ #t2. (Compromise( ) @ #t2) ⇒ ¬(#t2 < #t1))"
*/
