guarded formula characterizing all counter-examples:
"∃ CA fields rootCA ca_fields L1 L2 L #t1 #t2.
  (BrowserAcceptsChain( CA, fields, rootCA, ca_fields, L1, L2 ) @ #t1) ∧
  (CTTransparencyCheck( L, fields ) @ #t2)
